<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (tmly fạkr lmsẗ ạ̹ydyh .. why ḥạmlạny
 wqlby sẖạkr ḥbh wʿynyh .. ạlly ḥạrsạny)2
 (ạ̉nạ qlby fyk byṣdq .. kṭfl wḥdạny)2
 ạlqrạr- (mạfysẖ bḥwr tqdr kfạyẗ .. tfṣlny ʿn ḥbk
 mạfysẖ jbạl ʿạlyẗ fy smạyạ .. tʿly̱ ʿly̱ ḥbk)2
 (mạfysẖ tmn gẖạly .. ymnʿny ʿn ḥbk)2
 2- (ạ̹zạy ạ̉nạ ạ̉nsy̱ ṣlbk wmwtk .. ạlly njạny
 ạ̹zạy jldt wạ̹zạy dẖbḥt .. wklh ʿlsẖạny)2
 (ạ̉nạ qlby lyk mdywn .. fạlmsny mn tạny)2
 3- (ậsrny fyk ḥbk ly tẖạbt .. wʿmrh mạ ạtgẖyr
 jạdẖbny lyk ạ̹nk qạblny .. mhmạ bạ̉tʿyr)2
 (ạ̉jry ʿlyk wạtẖq .. wfy ḥḍnk ạ̉tgẖyr)2</lyrics>
<title>tmly fạkr</title>
</song>